{"tid":435412,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"車嘅常識 - 我問你答","createTime":"2017-10-14T09:11:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-21T06:00:01.000Z","uid":39230,"like":2,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"968bcef7464765bfa50c15152717fd3c6d307c3a","tid":435412,"uid":39230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T09:11:37.000Z","msg":"小弟雖然揸左大概十年車<br />\n但對車嘅認識仲係好少<br />\n好多術語都唔清唔楚<br />\n所以想請教吓大家<br />\n<br />\n咩叫直7？<br />\n細車 1L turbo 行直3，即係點<br />\n我知如果同 size 引擎直7慳油過直3<br />\n但個直字點解"},{"pid":"564d2f30fb9e9524427d0bb137a1de8d4d72a847","tid":435412,"uid":39230,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T09:16:13.000Z","msg":"唔記得講揸咩車<br />\n第一架係二手 Lancer 1.5 coupe 1999<br />\n比人爆賤賣左<br />\n<br />\n第二架係全新 CX-5 2016<br />\n<br />\n第三架 （買比女友但發我揸得仲多過佢）<br />\nCorolla 2015 demo option 齊晒咁上下"},{"pid":"c29c3e5fd0948edc2123250c06071b79307407ca","tid":435412,"uid":39230,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T09:19:02.000Z","msg":"波箱 dsg, vvt, etc 有咩分別"},{"pid":"2b838e90b21cb724388bdf944e2fa1e1a30eb626","tid":435412,"uid":39230,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T09:20:03.000Z","msg":"扭力又係乜<br />\n點影響車嘅性能"},{"pid":"6fb231a104e24a5515615eb8792519aefdfd4b14","tid":435412,"uid":138834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T09:55:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>扭力又係乜<br />\n點影響車嘅性能</blockquote><br />\n扭力係咩好難答wo<br />\n詳細就唔識答你<br />\n不過你可以理解做轉動嘅力量<br />\n扭力大，架車前進嘅力量就大<br />\n然後再透過齒比轉成換成車呔嘅轉速<br />\n唔知咁答有冇錯"},{"pid":"d348927d24ddc3ee6c53003f0933f0fc29d710e6","tid":435412,"uid":3937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T10:48:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E7%9B%B4%E5%88%97%E5%9B%9B%E7%BC%B8%E5%BC%95%E6%93%8E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E7%259B%25B4%25E5%2588%2597%25E5%259B%259B%25E7%25BC%25B8%25E5%25BC%2595%25E6%2593%258E&d=xl8qb1EPxtlhBa4