<br />\n嗰時想買部 swift 試吓</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nN波都會用油，因為你N波時引擎都繼續低轉緊。"},{"pid":"e6995234966a2174e2a8635154c483466c9e3de7","tid":435412,"uid":98567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T14:07:42.000Z","msg":"無知搭單一問<br />\n我想問呢 平時落大雨個倒後鏡 會睇得唔係好清楚 其實有冇野係買黎噴下個倒後鏡？"},{"pid":"43c399e336508314dde022faa5313e4a6b00fbdf","tid":435412,"uid":39230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T14:16:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無知搭單一問<br />\n我想問呢 平時落大雨個倒後鏡 會睇得唔係好清楚 其實有冇野係買黎噴下個倒後鏡？</blockquote><br />\n我之前買過一支野<br />\n可以搽落玻璃或鏡度防止起霧氣<br />\n但好似好麻煩<br />\n跟著我無理佢<br />\n<br />\n之後 Cx-5 同 Corolla 無呢個問題"},{"pid":"7591c5e7494626e35e3c960911a46523a9d0af49","tid":435412,"uid":39230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T14:18:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><br />\n係咪話 n 波唔會用油<br />\n早幾年已經講緊<br />\n嗰時想買部 swift 試吓</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nN波都會用油，因為你N波時引擎都繼續低轉緊。</blockquote><br />\n係囉，我都係咁諗<br />\n但嗰時佢賣到好行話0 consumption <br />\n我都唔知真定假<br />\n不過而家唔會買番細車<br />\n鍾意 SUV"},{"pid":"37e5e02ef7da168ec2a227356f33bfa1d109a1ae","tid":435412,"uid":129079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T23:58:21.000Z","msg":"[quote]扭力 加速既力度<br />\n馬力 速度既極限<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但係我想問下 拖頭有成四百幾匹 咁照呢個邏輯之下 係咪無拖架嘅情況下 起步好快？<br />\n<br />\n求賜教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4fd66acb6f2d189c50bda45018fbb87b73a0d4f","tid":435412,"uid":1992,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T00:21:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>以為返咗小學</blockquote><br />\n你小學有呢啲堂上<br />\n咩小學咁巴閉</blockquote><br />\n 依啲撚樣最興拋句出黎踩鳩人<br />\n然後扮到高高在上"},{"pid":"1a676ca03fa494f7291c017a7cd5cd2